What:		/sys/devices/platform/<platform>/fan_boost_mode
Date:		Sep 2019
KernelVersion:	5.3
Contact:	"Yurii Pavlovskyi" <yurii.pavlovskyi@gmail.com>
Description:
		Fan boost mode:
			* 0 - normal,
			* 1 - overboost,
			* 2 - silent

